window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Happy ever after is only the beginning.</p> <p>Find your fate between the lines in this collection of steamy and special romances from NYT best-selling author Carrie Ann Ryan.</p> <p>Fate can change in an instant.</p> <p>But love can be everlasting.</p> <p>Includes eight short stories and novellas never before in audio or print.</p> <ul> <li>What if It’s You (A Montgomery Ink Legacy Romance)</li> <li>Over the Bridge (A Montgomery Ink Legacy Romance)</li> <li>Was It Over Then (A Wilder Brothers Romance)</li> <li>Inked Kingdom (A Montgomery Ink Romance)</li> <li>Montgomery Midnight Kisses (A Montgomery Ink Romance)</li> <li>Inked Fantasy (A Montgomery Ink: Boulder Romance)</li> <li>A Very Montgomery Christmas (A Montgomery Ink: Boulder Romance)</li> <li>Delicate Nights (A Montgomery Ink Romance)</li> </ul>"; 
